  d/(b*c) \[Star] Subst[Int[SubstFor[(1+d^2*x^2)^((-n-1)/2),Sinh[c*(a+b*x)]/d,u,x],x],x,Sinh[c*(a+b*x)]/d] /;
 FunctionOfQ[Sinh[c*(a+b*x)]/d,u,x]] /;
FreeQ[{a,b,c},x] && IntegerQ[(n-1)/2] && NonsumQ[u]

